title: Google\Cloud\Core\AnonymousCredentials
name: AnonymousCredentials
description: Provides an anonymous set of credentials, which is useful for APIs which do not require authentication.

methods.name: fetchAuthToken
methods.description: Fetches the auth token. In this case it returns a null value.

methods.name: getCacheKey
methods.description: Returns the cache key. In this case it returns a null value, disabling caching.

methods.name: getLastReceivedToken
methods.description: Fetches the last received token. In this case, it returns the same null auth token.
